data.title: About me
data.content: JaP is kewl. tl;dr I post things that I create here. (But only the good ones.) I'm ${{var e=new Date,t=e.getFullYear(),n=e.getMonth(),a=e.getDate(),r=t-2003-1;return(n>10||10==n&&a>=28)&&r++,r}} years old (I'm in high school) and I like to create things. I've been creating things since July 2016. I use this site so that I can show off to other people. Including showing off the site. Since I'm showing off the site, I only include the projects that will make it seem like I'm good at what I do, and hide away all of the terrible and unfinished stuff.
